WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:02.020
Carbon dioxide gets the headlines

2
00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:05.760
But cutting methane thirty percent by 2030 could

3
00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:08.200
