4
00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:09.280
by 2040

5
00:00:09.968 --> 00:00:12.940
Phasing down HFC refrigerants could avoid up to

6
00:00:12.940 --> 00:00:15.720
another zero point five degrees by 2100

7
00:00:16.920 --> 00:00:18.760
That is huge near-term leverage

8
00:00:19.640 --> 00:00:22.140
Here is the twist both targets depend on

9
00:00:22.140 --> 00:00:23.740
materials we do not have yet

10
00:00:24.470 --> 00:00:27.460
We need catalysts that convert stranded methane without

11
00:00:27.460 --> 00:00:30.180
