12
00:00:30.580 --> 00:00:32.900
safe and low-warming all at once

13
00:00:33.980 --> 00:00:36.420
Fast atomistic AI should help search the options

14
00:00:37.280 --> 00:00:39.960
Except its biggest errors happen exactly where these

15
00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:44.820
materials work surfaces transition states radical fragments and

16
00:00:44.820 --> 00:00:45.600
phase boundaries

17
00:00:46.560 --> 00:00:50.320
In those under-coordinated environments universal models can soften

18
00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:53.140
