38
00:01:48.580 --> 00:01:53.400
Across thirty-six blind model-and-material combinations corrected predictions reached

39
00:01:53.400 --> 00:01:56.000
a correlation of zero point nine zero six

40
00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:58.240
with zero adjustable parameters

41
00:01:59.280 --> 00:02:02.680
Methane catalysts and next-generation cooling are not separate

42
00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:03.780
discovery stories

43
00:02:04.580 --> 00:02:07.360
They share one hidden error geometry and one

44
00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:09.900
